snippet.title: DEMCAD
snippet.description: Gun reviews, current events, emergency preparation and the second amendment. My name is Reginald Kaigler and I've dedicated this channel to raising the public's awareness about disaster preparation. I upload videos that cover many aspects of emergency preparation (i.e. storing and filtering water, security, storing food, communication, dealing with threats and helping the community).
